{
  "stem": "7302.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My parents was telling me the story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the first war, World War, when they starting to shoot the bomb, it was hanging in the shul, and it isn't--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Explode.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And who was coming to visit this from overseas-- people, they always were showing this place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was an underground that was taking you-- that people have been hiding in the first war, World War.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it, it-- it was like industry, not much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a [NON-ENGLISH] you know, that they was wood-cutting.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Others, I don't really recall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We haven't been rich, but we haven't been poor, but I knew that I was having.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a very quiet life, a [NON-ENGLISH] life-- you know about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in 1939.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russian-- the Russian was taking over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like Poland, it was divided.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the Germans was taking-- starting to go in on one side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then the Russians started to go in the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have been close to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one night, we, we went to sleep with the Polish people in the morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We, we woke up, it was all the Russian people there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole army was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they started to make all those changes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took away from the stores all the goods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- it was very hard with the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't get any food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to stay in lines for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was bad, in one way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other way, like cultural things, it wasn't bad, because they started to educate people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They wanted to make lots of schools.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We was having cultural clubs, like, they were showing films, and they-- and they started to make schools for all who never went to school.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
